data.description: This stunning custom home is everything you want in a lake house and also everything you would require in a full time residence. It features beautiful wood floors, an open floor plan and floor to ceiling windows and doors that center around the picturesque lake views and peacefulness of this quiet, deep water cove.The bar looks over into a dream kitchen with custom shaker cabinets and granite tops and island.The generous office space can also be a formal dining room, while the dining area in the family room looks out onto the huge screened porch.The master suite also walks out onto the screened porch and has a gorgeous tiled walk-in shower. With 3 bedrooms downstairs, you may also use the 2 flex rooms upstairs as additional guest rooms giving the potential of a 5 bedroom home.The current owners use the upstairs as entertainment and hobby areas because of their massive size. Outside, you'll find 200 feet of water frontage framed by a key stone retaining wall, new composite decking on the private dock with boat slip and a modern tiered walkway. In addition to the 3 car garage, there are 2 detached carports, workshop and a 20x40 covered RV storage on a concrete pad with 30 amp hookup. The home has a propane fireplace and a whole house Generac generator. The home and foundation are fully out of the flood plain and the owner has an assumable VA loan currently at 2.25%! This home has it all!! Located conveniently halfway between Charlotte and Columbia, it is great for commuters!
